This plugin implements a SpringRTS lobby server operating in LAN mode (no
account registration required). It makes it possible to run SPADS autonomously,
without having to connect to an external lobby server.

The AnyEvent Perl module is required for this plugin, it can be installed
easily as follows:
  - for Windows:
      cpanm -n AnyEvent
  - for Debian/Ubuntu based Linux distributions:
      sudo apt-get install libanyevent-perl
  - for RedHat/Fedora/CentOS based Linux distributions:
      sudo dnf install perl-AnyEvent
  - for Linux distributions without precompiled package for AnyEvent module:
      sudo cpan AnyEvent
